  <brief_title>Lipid Profile in Patients With Severe Sepsis or Septic Shock Under Strict or Liberal Glycemic Control</brief_title>
  <official_title>Tight Glycemic Control and Sepsis Related Dyslipidemia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
